reviews.review_text: Excellent show and recording Tonight Chuck Berry died. Someone called into the studio while I was doing my radio show and asked for the Around and Around from this concert. I knew for a post-Hornsby show I had to go AUD, and this recording did not fail. Thanks for taping and transferring!
